name: U.F.O (Unidentified Fishing Operation)
description:
Have you ever wanted to be a UFO??

well too bad because you're a drone sent by a UFO to catch and sell fish to appease the humans (and the fish god but we don't talk about that). Fly around as fast as you can with your hook to catch as many fish before the shop opens and humans find you.

All assets were created  by me

uses unity engine

Fullscreen mode is HIGHLY RECCOMENDED
